		<gravity>0 -9.8066499999999994 0</gravity>
		
		<credits>Full-body model adapted from Rajagopal et al. No muscles included. Removed patella. Added contact spheres. Free pelvis translation, added ball joint between head and torso, locked arm pronation/supination, clamped hip flexion to 150° instead of 120°, hip adduction -60° instead of -50°, hip rotation -70° instead of -40°, knee 155° instead of 120°.</credits>
		
		<publications>Pagnon, D., Domalain, M., Reveret, L. (2021). Pose2Sim: An End-to-End Workflow for 3D Markerless Sports Kinematics—Part 1: Robustness. Sensors, 21(19), 6530.</publications>
		
